<br>
Now I think our biggest problem is the number of spells we have to get.  Our focus items should all be vendor sold, I would prefer that to having our 61 Bolt vendor sold.  Why try to get 5 spells by turn in when at 63 we can get a single spell that summons all of these?  A large waste requiring the magician community to need more parchments than most any other class.  There is one plus side to this though.  Magicians are staying in on etherial drops rolls longer than the other classes.  The magician market is flooded with certain spells making them very cheap to buy.  I have summon choker I finally gave away.  Level 61/62 spells have droped from 20k to 5k in a matter of 2 weeks.<br>
<br>
Kopla<br>
